@chatBase = http://localhost:8003/api/v1
@authToken = user_token_123

### Listar chats (paginado)
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Listar chats — filtrar por nombre
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/?search=proyecto
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Listar chats — ordenar y filtrar por tags (ALL deben coincidir)
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/?ordering=-created_at&tags=work,urgent
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Listar chats creados por mí
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/me/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Listar chats archivados
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/archived/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Crear chat
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Proyecto Alpha",
  "system_prompt": "Eres un asistente experto en análisis de documentos.",
  "response_style": "Responde de forma concisa y estructurada.",
  "tags": ["trabajo", "documentos"]
}


### Detalle de un chat
GET {{chatBase}}/chats/1/
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Actualizar chat (partial update)
PATCH {{chatBase}}/chats/1/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Proyecto Alpha v2",
  "tags": ["trabajo", "documentos", "urgente"]
}


### Eliminar chat — responde 204
DELETE {{chatBase}}/chats/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Archivar uno o varios chats
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/archive/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "ids": [1, 2, 3]
}


### Desarchivar uno o varios chats
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/unarchive/
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "ids": [1, 2, 3]
}


### Pinear chat — responde 204
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/1/pin/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Despinear chat — responde 204
DELETE {{chatBase}}/chats/1/pin/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Bloquear chat (solo owner) — responde 204
POST {{chatBase}}/chats/1/lock/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### Desbloquear chat — responde 204
DELETE {{chatBase}}/chats/1/lock/
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

